      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a solid, dependable car that\u2019s been well-cared for. Everything runs smoothly, the interior is nice and comfy, and it's totally ready for its next adventure! I've loved every mile in this car, and I'm sure you will too. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
