    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This unit boasts an 8,000 RPM redline and linear power delivery via its factory individual throttle body setup. Torque is managed through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock for precise corner exits. The chassis has been proactively addressed with documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. Fitted with Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, the suspension geometry remains tight, offering the communicative feedback this platform is legendary for. A well-sorted, driver-centric example ready for the tarmac.",
