    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2016 BMW M235i Coupe, a true driver\u2019s car that strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily comfort. Finished in a sophisticated Mineral Grey Metallic, the exterior remains in wonderful shape, retaining a high-gloss finish with only minor stone chips on the lower front valance consistent with light road use. The interior is a non-smoker cabin featuring Black Dakota leather that has been regularly conditioned; the seat bolsters are firm and show very little signs of ingress wear. All technological features, from the navigation system to the heated seats and Harman Kardon audio, are fully operational. Under the hood, the 3.0L TwinPower Turbo inline-six runs smoothly, backed by a comprehensive service history and a recent professional multi-point inspection. The vehicle sits on Michelin Pilot Sport tires with roughly 70% tread life remaining, and the braking system feels sharp and responsive. This car has been garage-kept and loved, offering the next owner a turn-key experience with no immediate maintenance required. Includes two sets of keys and the original owner's portfolio.",
